        <div class="exercise">
            <p><b>Question 3 (Tricky!):</b> Base = 6 cm, Slanted Side = 7 cm, Height = 4 cm.</p>
            <p><i>Hint: Ignore the slanted side!</i></p>
            <input type="number" id="q3" placeholder="Area?">
            <button onclick="checkAnswer(3, 24)">Check</button>
